payload.message:
对，继续上完整 JSON。这里我把 `skills` 和 `plugins` 放在同一个例子里看，因为 target/scope 是横切字段。

**A. 全局默认 + 单项覆盖，我推荐这个**

```json
{
  "version": 1,
  "targets": ["codex"],
  "scope": "project",
  "skills": {
    "grill-me": {
      "source": "./.agents/skills/grille-me"
    },
    "frontend-review": {
      "source": "github:acme/agent-skills",
      "ref": "main",
      "path": "skills/frontend-review"
    }
  },
  "plugins": {
    "browser-use": {
      "source": "github:acme/agent-plugins",
      "ref": "main",
      "path": "plugins/browser-use"
    },
    "linear": {
      "source": "github:acme/agent-plugins",
      "ref": "main",
      "path": "plugins/linear",
      "targets": ["codex", "claude-code"],
      "scope": "user"
    }
  }
}
```

含义：默认都装到 Codex、project scope；`linear` 是例外，装到 Codex 和 Claude Code，且用 user scope。

**B. 每个条目都写 targets/scope**

```json
{
  "version": 1,
  "skills": {
    "grill-me": {
      "source": "./.agents/skills/grille-me",
      "targets": ["codex"],
      "scope": "project"
    },
    "frontend-review": {
      "source": "github:acme/agent-skills",
      "ref": "main",
      "path": "skills/frontend-review",
      "targets": ["codex"],
      "scope": "project"
    }
  },
  "plugins": {
    "browser-use": {
      "source": "github:acme/agent-plugins",
      "ref": "main",
      "path": "plugins/browser-use",
      "targets": ["codex"],
      "scope": "project"
    }
  }
}
```

含义：最明确，但每一项都重复，手写会烦。

**C. JSON 不写 targets/scope，只靠命令行**

```json
{
  "version": 1,
  "skills": {
    "grill-me": {
      "source": "./.agents/skills/grille-me"
    }
  },
  "plugins": {
    "browser-use": {
      "source": "github:acme/agent-plugins",
      "path": "plugins/browser-use"
    }
  }
}
```

然后靠：

```bash
ai-pkgs install --target codex --scope project
```

含义：文件更像“依赖列表”，但别人拿到仓库后，光靠 `ai-package.json` 不能完整复现安装策略。

我推荐 A，因为它最接近 package manager：文件里有默认策略，单项可以 override。

