# ai-package.json 安装追踪

> 涉及目录: `cli-core/src/types/package/`, `cli-core/src/core/package/`

---

## 1. 文件位置

| 级别 | 路径 | 触发条件 |
|------|------|----------|
| 项目级 | `./ai-package.json`（项目根目录） | `ai-labs xxx add -p` 或 默认 `--project` |
| 全局级 | `~/.ai-labs/ai-package.json` | `ai-labs xxx add -g` |

项目级可纳入 Git（由用户决定）。

---

## 2. 完整类型定义

新增文件: `cli-core/src/types/package/index.ts`

```typescript
// ── 安装来源 ──
export type InstallSource = 'marketplace' | 'local';

// ── 单组件安装记录 ──
export type ComponentEntry = {
  version: string;
  source: InstallSource;
  installedAt: string; // ISO 8601
  files: Array<string>; // 安装到磁盘的文件路径列表（相对项目根）
  // 合并类型（mcp, hooks）需要追踪写入了哪些 key 到哪个文件
  mergedKeys?: Record<string, Array<string>>;
  // 例如: { ".cursor/mcp.json": ["github", "postgres"] }
};

// ── Plugin 安装记录 ──
export type PluginEntry = {
  version: string;
  source: InstallSource;
  installedAt: string;
  // Plugin 包含的每种组件类型的文件列表
  skills: Array<string>;
  rules: Array<string>;
  subagents: Array<string>;
  commands: Array<string>;
  hooks: Array<string>;
  mcp: Array<string>;
  // 合并追踪
  mergedMcp: Record<string, Array<string>>;
  // 例如: { ".cursor/mcp.json": ["plugin-mcp-server"] }
  mergedHooks: Record<string, Array<string>>;
  // 例如: { ".cursor/hooks.json": ["onSave", "onStart"] }
};

// ── 根结构 ──
export type AiPackage = {
  version: 1;
  plugins: Record<string, PluginEntry>;
  components: {
    skills: Record<string, ComponentEntry>;
    mcp: Record<string, ComponentEntry>;
    rules: Record<string, ComponentEntry>;
    subagents: Record<string, ComponentEntry>;
    hooks: Record<string, ComponentEntry>;
    commands: Record<string, ComponentEntry>;
  };
};
```

